TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: Select A.ADDRESS_DIM_SID,A.PARTICIPANT_ID, A.ADDRESS_LINE_ONE, A.ADDRESS_LINE_TWO, A.ADDRESS_LINE_THREE, A.BAD_ADDRESS_IND, A.CITY_NAME, A.COUNTRY_TYPE_NAME, A.COUNTY_NAME, A.EFT_WAIVER_TYPE_NAME, A.EMAIL_ADDRESS_ID, A.FMS_ADDRESS_CODE_TEXT, A.FOREIGN_POSTAL_CODE, A.LOCATION_NAME, A.MILITARY_POSTAL_TYPE_CODE, A.MILITARY_POST_OFFICE_TYPE_CODE, A.POSTAL_CODE, A.PROVINCE_NAME, A.PARTICIPANT_ADDRESS_ID, A.PARTICIPANT_ADDRESS_TYPE_NAME, A.TREASURY_SEQUENCE_NUMBER, A.TERRITORY_NAME, A.ZIP_PREFIX_NUMBER, A.ZIP_FIRST_SUFFIX_NUMBER, A.ZIP_SECOND_SUFFIX_NUMBER, A.TREASURY_ADDRESS_LINE_ONE, A.TREASURY_ADDRESS_LINE_TWO, A.TREASURY_ADDRESS_LINE_THREE, A.TREASURY_ADDRESS_LINE_FOUR, A.TREASURY_ADDRESS_LINE_FIVE, A.TREASURY_ADDRESS_LINE_SIX, A.SHARED_ADDRESS_IND, A.ADDRESS_EFFECTIVE_DATE, A.ADDRESS_END_DATE, A.ADDRESS_TYPE, A.STATE_NAME, A.COUNTRY_CODE, A.CRC_NUMBER, A.BEGIN_EFFECTIVE_DATE, A.END_EFFECTIVE_DATE, A.CURRENT_RECORD_IND, A.DW_LOAD_DATE, A.ADDRESS_VALID_GEO_DIM_SID, A.GEOCODING_STATUS, A.CONGRESSTIONAL_DISTRICT, A.MAIL_SCORE, A.MATCH_CODE, A.ZIP_9DIGIT, A.POST_CD_NEW, B.SSN From ADDRESS_DIM A JOIN PERSON_DIM B ON A.PARTICIPANT_ID=B.PARTICIPANT_IDENTIFIER WHERE B.EFFECTIVE_STATUS_INDICATOR='Y' AND A.CURRENT_RECORD_IND='Y'
